Class SearchExecutor

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.QueryExecutor
au.csiro.pathling.search.SearchExecutor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IBundleProvider
public class SearchExecutor extends au.csiro.pathling.QueryExecutor implements IBundleProvider
Encapsulates the execution of a search query, implemented as an IBundleProvider for integration into the HAPI mechanism for returning paged search results.
